        <abstract> 
<p>Asks JM whether he will publish 750 copies of a pamphlet [Chauncey Wright’s review of Mivart’s <hi rend="italic">Genesis of species</hi>, <hi rend="italic">North Am. Rev.</hi> 113 (1871): 63–103] at CD’s expense.</p>  
<p>Has been ill so cannot say when he will finish new edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p>  
<p>Asks about sales and printing of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
